Software Dolibarr is described as Open source solution for all around business management: Sales, Invoicing, Agenda, Stock, Purchase Orders, Emailing, Accounting, Expense report, Leave requests. Several hundreds of modules are available according to your need..Features included: Accounting, Billing and Invoicing, Business Management, CRM, Contract Management, Enterprise Resource Planning, Expense Report, Financial CRM, Lead Management, Online CRM, Order Management, Predictive Lead Scoring, Product Management, Purchasing, Quoting, Recurring Billing, Sales Force Automation, Stock Portfolio Management, Vendor Management, Warehouse Management. Pricing described as Free if installed "On premise".
From 9 euros / month with a Saas provider and a target audience Thanks to its modularity (several hundred of business modules), Dolibarr meets the needs of any type of business of any size.